title: Volleyball Roundup: Ridgewood wins pair
text:
Volleyball Roundup: Ridgewood wins pair 11:21 p.m. EDT October 10, 2015 CONNECT TWEET LINKEDIN COMMENT EMAIL MORE 
Ridgewood Tri 
Ridgewood (16-3, 12-1) host a tri match Saturday and defeated Indian Valley 25-12, 25-19 and Dover 25-12, 25-21. In the win over Indian Valley, Laura Crawford had 21 kills, four digs and three blocks; Allie Dobson had seven kills and five blocks; Eliza Haynes had 23 assists, three kills, six digs and one ace; Morgan McDorman had nine digs and one ace and Sydney Zinkon had 15 assists. 
In the win over Dover, Crawford had 12 kills, nine digs, two blocks and one ace; Haynes had 12 assists, three kills, one block and seven digs; Dobson had two kills, thee blocks and one ace; Autumn Brown had four kills and one block; and McDorman had 10 digs.
